title: [Vilorcasdra's Outfitting]
[Vilorcasdra's Weaponry]
description: Beneath an elegantly arched fel ceiling, a vaalorian crested pennant hangs on one of the textured red silk walls.  An elegantly carved oak armoire and a gold-veined black marble counter sit in opposite corners while a suit of golden armor rests on a parquet golden oak floor.
